Original Title: Robert Plant and the Sensational Space Shifters: Live at David Lynch's Festival of Disruption

================================================================================
Robert.Plant.and.The.Sensational.Space.Shifters.2018.BluRay.BD25.AVC.DTS-HD.MA.5.1
================================================================================



Robert Plant has formed his current band The Sensational Space Shifters in 2012 and has been recording and touring with them ever since. Robert Plant has always introduced music from many cultures into his work and mixing Sensational Space Shifters with African rhythms and melodies, rock and folk roots is his latest incarnation. In October 2016, they attended the David Lynch Inaugural Breakout Festival at the Ace Hotel Theater in Los Angeles, an event that raised funds for the David Lynch Foundation. The set featured tracks from the band's 2014 album Lullaby and ... The Ceaseless Roar alongside fascinating reworks from Space Shifters from Led Zeppelin classics. The performance gets a sweeping reception from crowded theater audiences and is now released on DVD.
 
Line-up: Robert Plant, Justin Adams, Liam Skin Tyson, John Baggott, Juldeh Camara, Billy Fuller and Dave Smith.


1. Poor Howard
